snippet.title: Kaiju Girls [Tease Trailer][RPG / Monster Girls]
snippet.description:
Kaiju Girls is a RPG full of Monster Girls. The protagonist lost his memory in an accident and became a KaijuTamer, with the Kaiju girls in the Kaiju world full of danger adventure! In the wonderful and exciting adventure journey in the protagonist will slowly recall his memories.

#kaijugirls #rpg #monster
